  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose is to determine the effective dosage and to study the effects of this dosage
      taken for 12 days on systolic and diastolic blood pressure in patients with hypertension.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      1. Office seated peripheral systolic and diastolic blood pressure

        2. Adverse events and vital signs

        3. Plasma concentrations of SLx-2101
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
